{"tid":2499634,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"同時俾同一個「快遞沒人領取」電話打去我兩個電話","createTime":"2021-04-22T04:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T05:19:08.000Z","uid":393322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f7c5ad6c6a9cec92701bd77cb6e954123edf2224","tid":2499634,"uid":393322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:55:53.000Z","msg":"我本身有兩個電話號碼，一個工作用一個私人用<br />\n<br />\n而我工作用嗰個電話好少攞嚟登記啲咩嘅<br />\n<br />\n咁我都和呢啲呃人電話係會隨機咁call人<br />\n<br />\n咁佢打嚟，我梗係唔聽啦<br />\n<br />\n但係1秒後，我第二部電話就有同一個電話號碼打嚟<br />\n<br />\n我當時嚇咗嚇，點解會同一個電話號碼打嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽咗之後又係嗰啲快遞冇人領取嘅電話<br />\n<br />\n咁究竟佢係知道呢兩個電話係同一個人嘅，定係純粹真係咁岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWX1ggrdQ45bnNgqo3tqjzcPyjYq6L2DsS91P1zAGMacS?filename=admJpmw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FadmJpmw.png&h=8851353e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWkYzwJcrNCf9jkLicQWk2maoYAQZb7X4e7dbLb8F233q?filename=dMzVZUR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdMzVZUR.png&h=9875d5d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd345ba4b757d3f412c6843c25d1ffafd8b25df3","tid":2499634,"uid":329698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:56:46.000Z","msg":"仲以為係講故台"},{"pid":"9d80029c3a7c7fffb217b63dd20bdc92a32d10ca","tid":2499634,"uid":393322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd345ba4b757d3f412c6843c25d1ffafd8b25df3","tid":2499634,"uid":329698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:56:46.000Z","msg":"仲以為係講故台"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:58:06.000Z","msg":"我認真架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b50a82b739883b6a93da02c87b28946607d190","tid":2499634,"uid":22535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:59:51.000Z","msg":"你已經被人盯上<i